Concrètement à Giroux .	Specifically by Giroux .
En coopération avec Jagr il marqua trois buts , ensuite Wayne Simmonds transforma un quatrième but .	After assist with Jágr , he scored the third goal ; consequently , his shot was touched into a fourth goal by Wayne Simmonds .
